<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="when-pron">when <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wen/    美 /wen/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1since-until-till">1.<strong>[疑问代词，用作since, until, till等介词的宾语]什么时候：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Till when can you stay?
你能待到什么时候？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[关系代词] 那时：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We came back on Tuesday, since when we have been working in the repair shop. 
我们星期二回来的，从那时起就一直在修理车间工作。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The last time we had great fun was <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ we were visiting the Water Park.  （2008 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. when  </p></div>